<blockquote>
<p><strong>The Sacred Djehuti</strong><br />
<strong>Authors:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580837144" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580837144" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;">Ayers</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p>Part 8 of the <strong>Team Bird</strong> storyline. The bird god himself! We're not done yet &#8212; we're coming for you, End of Death! Hub:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/bird">Team Bird Hub</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<p>This has been in the drafting process longer than any other article we've written for this contest. But it's finally here! Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580837144" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;">Ayers</a></span> for being an excellent co-author and pitching some insane ideas while we were writing this. And thanks to my teammates for being great, as always.</p>
